## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources consulted. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the rapidly changing nature of socio-economic conditions can affect the relevance of the findings. Additionally, the report primarily focuses on developed countries, which may not fully represent global trends. Further research could include more diverse geographic perspectives and longitudinal studies to better understand long-term trends.